channel.title: How To Change The Home Teleport And Other Teleports?
channel.description: [size=24pt]How To Change The Home Teleport And Other Teleports? when i click home in magic book it's take me to camolet how do i change it to edge-village please help ! [/size]

item.title: How To Change The Home Teleport And Other Teleports?
item.dc:creator: @iDontRun iDontRun
item.description:
@iDontRun wrote:

To change the home of a player when they loggin in
1.) Go to Client.java and search Initial X and Y, the change the coords of it to your new one, then compile thats done.
2.) Changing the home teleport location, Go to clickingmost.java and search Case 4140, change the X and Y of it to your home teleport location, compile and your done.
Hope it helps, this is for DeltaScape Based servers it should work for most other unless its devo.
